    <!-- Contact Us -->
    <table class="container">
      <tr>
        <td>
          <table class="row">
            <tr>
              <td class="wrapper offset-by-one">
                <table class="ten columns">
                  <tr>
                    <td class="center welcome">
<p>Hi {{{$name}}},</p>

<p>
  Welcome to the Razorpay family.
  <br>
  In order for us to take you live, here are the next steps and timelines:
</p>

<h3>KYC Process</h3>

<p>The first step involves filling up the activation form on the <a href="https://dashboard.razorpay.com">Razorpay Dashboard</a>. The list of documents and details required for us to take you live can be found then in the <a href="https://dashboard.razorpay.com/#/app/activation">Activation</a> panel. All requirements have a basic explanation alongside to help you through the process.

<p>This process is crucial as we share the same KYC with our partner banks who do their own due diligence. Also, signing up allows you to <a href="https://dashboard.razorpay.com/#/app/keys">generate test keys</a> from our dashboard which can be used for integrating payments in your product. You can just swap your test keys with your live keys once your account is activated.</p>

<h3>API Integration</h3>

<p>In parallel, you can start integrating our API with your product. Various integrations (including Mobile SDKs and Plugins) are available at <a href="https://razorpay.com/integrations">razorpay.com/integrations</a>. The API documentation is available at <a href="https://docs.razorpay.com/">docs.razorpay.com</a>. Feel free to drop a mail at <a href="https://dashboard.razorpay.com/#/app/dashboard#request">here</a> in case of any queries.</p>

<h3>Activation Timeline</h3>

<p>As soon as the KYC Process in completed by you, depending on the business segment, we will take you live in the upcoming 2-3 days.</p>

<p>
  Cheers,
  <br>
  Team Razorpay
</p>
                    </td>
                    <td class="expander"></td>
                  </tr>
